title: KGAR 8x4x2ft Metal Raised Garden Bed Outdoor Garden Raised Planter Box for Vegetables Flowers Herbs, Dark Grey
feature_bullets: [" ✿【More Spacious Planting Space】This metal plant bed measure is 94.1\"L x 47.2\"W x 23.6\"H. This large flower planter box provide ample growing space to raise vegetables, herbs, flowers and plants. 23.6 inches depth gives enough capacity to hold soil."," ✿【Less bending and stronger roots】Our raised garden bed planter offer 23.6 inch tall, which provides greater drainage and root growth, compared to typical raised beds, which are between 12 and 15 inches tall or less. Deep-rooted fruits and vegetables like watermelons, sweet potatoes, pumpkins, and others are ideal for planting. The 17\" tall design requires less stooping and shields plants from rabbits, animals, and dogs."," ✿【Durable Metal Planter Box】The metal planter raised beds with anti-rust coating allow to expose to sun, rain, snow and so on for a long time. Thickened steel and reinforced corners that allows it to support the weight of the garden bed itself, soil and plants."," ✿【Various Uses】Our planter-raised beds are ideal for growing vegetables, fruits, herbs, and other plants in your garden or yard, helping you create a beautiful garden."," ✿【Easy Installation】The above ground garden bed is equipped with complete accessories, including bolts and nuts. Just connect the plates with screws. You can finish the installation in a few minutes."]
